			<h3>company history</h3>
			<p>Marpatt was founded by Olive and Richard Koeberle (Chairman & Managing Director respectively). Realising there was a gap in the UK Kitchen market for high quality wooden kitchen components trading began in 1977.As with all true family companies not many years passed before Sons Patrick and Mark joined to take on roles in Sales,servicing the growing client base.</p>
			<p>Ideally suited for distribution and coincidently the family home city, Marpatt has and probably will always be based in Leicester,it’s new head quarters being perfectly situated to Leicester’s main ring road.</p>
